OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FThe first repatriation flight to leave
OL,8,Fthe Middle East will leave Oman on
OL,9,FWednesday evening as the government
OL,10,Fscrambles to evacuate citizens from
OL,11,Fthe region as the war with Iran enters
OL,12,Fits fifth day.
OL,14,FThe Foreign Office said the flight
OL,15,Fwill depart the country's capital,
OL,16,FMuscat, at 7pm and is available for
OL,17,FBritish nationals, their partners and
OL,18,Fchildren under 18 with a valid travel
OL,19,Fdocument.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer will face questions
OL,8,Fin the Commons on Wednesday over his
OL,9,Fdecisions on the unfolding Iran
OL,10,Fconflict, after Donald Trump unleashed
OL,11,Ffresh criticism of the prime minister.
OL,13,FPriority for the evacuation flight
OL,14,Fwill be given to the most vulnerable
OL,15,Fand they will contact British
OL,16,Fnationals in Oman. Anyone who
OL,17,Fregistered their presence in the
OL,18,FUnited Arab Emirates (UAE) and are now
OL,19,Fin Oman is asked to register for a
OL,20,Fplace on a flight, according to the
OL,21,FForeign Office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FThe department asked people not to
OL,8,Ftravel to Muscat International Airport
OL,9,Fin Oman unless they are contacted by
OL,10,Fofficials, while dependents who are
OL,11,Fnot British nationals will require a
OL,12,Fvalid visa or permission to enter or
OL,13,Fremain granted for more than three
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,16,FSome 130,000 Britons have registered
OL,17,Ftheir presence in the Middle East, as
OL,18,Fthe Foreign Office said it was working
OL,19,Fwith airlines on more routes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FThe US president on Tuesday said
OL,8,FStarmer was "not Winston Churchill" in
OL,9,Fhis latest rebuke of the prime
OL,10,Fminister, who did not allow American
OL,11,Fplanes to launch their initial strikes
OL,12,Fagainst Tehran from British bases.
OL,14,FStarmer announced Britain would send
OL,15,FHMS Dragon, one of the Royal Navy's
OL,16,Fsix Type 45 air defence destroyers, to
OL,17,Fdefend Cyprus after RAF Akrotiri was
OL,18,Fhit by a drone.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FThe war between Iran and the USA, now
OL,8,Fin its fifth day, will likely dominate
OL,9,Fthe agenda when Starmer enters the
OL,10,FCommons at noon on Wednesday for Prime
OL,11,FMinister's Questions.
OL,13,FStarmer decided on Sunday that UK
OL,14,Fbases, including the joint UK-US Diego
OL,15,FGarcia site in the Chagos Islands and
OL,16,FRAF Fairford in Gloucestershire, could
OL,17,Fbe used in the conflict, but only so
OL,18,Fthe US can strike defensively to
OL,19,Fprotect countries being targeted by
OL,20,FTehran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FHMS Dragon is being readied to depart
OL,8,Ffor the Mediterranean and will be
OL,9,Faccompanied by two Wildcat helicopters
OL,10,Fequipped with so-called "drone
OL,11,Fbusting" Martlet missiles, so it can
OL,12,Fprotect Britain's bases in Cyprus.
OL,14,FThe warship, which is emblazoned with
OL,15,Fthe Welsh red dragon on its prow, was
OL,16,Fpictured on Tuesday night at the Upper
OL,17,FHarbour Ammunition Facility (UHAF) in
OL,18,FPortsmouth harbour.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
