PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FThe Foreign Office updated its travel
OL,8,Fadvice for Thailand early on Wednesday
OL,9,F"due to the escalation in the Middle
OL,10,FEast".
OL,12,FIt said in a statement: "Escalation in
OL,13,Fthe Middle East has caused widespread
OL,14,Ftravel disruption, including airspace
OL,15,Fclosures, delayed and cancelled
OL,16,Fflights.
OL,18,F"Your travel plans may be affected,
OL,19,Feven if your destination is not in the
OL,20,FMiddle East."
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@EO]tD@YOUzD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
