OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FAffected British nationals are urged
OL,13,Fto stay across the latest updates from
OL,14,Ftheir airline or tour operator and
OL,15,Freview their travel insurance policies
OL,16,Fbefore travelling.
OL,18,FElsewhere, the UK Maritime Trade
OL,19,FOperations Centre (UKMTO) said a
OL,20,Fvessel had been struck by a projectile
OL,21,Foff the coast of Fujairah in the UAE.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
