PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772629886
OL,3,CFirst UK government repatriation
OL,4,Cflight to leave Middle East on
OL,5,CWednesday
OL,7,FIt said in a statement early on
OL,8,FWednesday: "UKMTO has received a
OL,9,Freport of an incident 7NM east of
OL,10,FFujairah, United Arab Emirates.
OL,12,F"The Master reported the vessel being
OL,13,Fstruck by an unknown projectile
OL,14,Fcausing damage to the steel plating.
OL,15,FThere has been no fire or water
OL,16,Fintake. All crew reported safe.
OL,18,F"Authorities are investigating.
OL,19,FVessels are advised to transit with
OL,20,Fcaution and report any suspicious
OL,21,Factivity to UKMTO."
OL,26,@pD@LOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
